title: Kim Kardashian West birthday: The stunning reality star turns 35 today
text:
Kim Kardashian West birthday: The stunning reality star turns 35 today By Maggie Davis on October 21, 2015 at 2:09 AM Comments The popular reality star Kim Kardashian West has turned a year older today. The stunning wife of Kanye West was born on October 21, 1980 to parents Robert and Kris. The star who was the highest paid reality television personality in 2010 was born as Kimberly Noel Kardashian in Los Angeles, California. Kim first managed to capture media attention through her camaraderie with Paris Hilton. Kim is not just a reality star. She is a social media personality, a stunning model and an actress. Kim’s siblings include Kourtney, Khloé and Rob. She even has step-brother and half-sisters who are also the renowned face of media. Kim is also widely known for her relationships in the past. But the star received wider notice post 2003 sex tape with former boyfriend Ray J. Kim tied the knot with the American Rapper Kanye West on May 24, 2014. The couple has a daughter North West and soon they are expecting a boy in December 2015. Kim confirmed the news of her second child through the photo sharing site Instagram. (ALSO READ: Kim Kardashian West birthday: 35 pictures of the reality star who turns a year older today) Kim is much excited to celebrate her special day with family and near and dear ones. Amidst the star studded party, Kim still recollects the traditions that were followed in the past. She reveals, “I had a birthday party when I was little with Morley the Clown. After that, my dad would call and leave the song as a voicemail and hang up,” reports InStyle. When North’s mommy was questioned what was she looking forward on her 35 th birthday she said, “Expanding the family, having a son and getting skinny,” reports Dailymail.com. We wish the best to the reality star who is all thrilled to celebrate her 35 th birthday! (ALSO READ: Kim Kardashian claims pregnancy is the ‘worst thing’ happened to her!)
